A minimalistic illustration featuring three large, softly overlapping translucent circles in warm harmonious colors—coral pink, golden yellow, and sage green—floating against a clean cream background. At the precise center where all three circles intersect, a tiny, content figure sits cross-legged in a meditative pose, bathed in the luminous glow created by the overlapping colors. The circles cast subtle shadows beneath them, giving depth to the composition. Small abstract shapes like gentle curved lines and dots drift around the edges, suggesting movement and possibility. The overall feeling is serene, balanced, and hopeful—a visual metaphor for finding one's sweet spot in life.
